        "ability keywords": "area of effect::evasive::fixed::movement::strong projectile::swap reloads",
        "ability details": "* Bike can be steered by aiming and sharper turns can be made with left and right directional inputs. The bike can jump, and pressing backward button can reduce the bike movement speed.\n* Launching the bike while in air, has a short targeting period, during which the jump gains some extra height, and Shion can move laterally at regular walking speed and redirect the launch. Holding the button extends the targeting period for up 1.5 seconds.\n* Activating <span class=\"ability-tooltip\" data-ability=\"Evade\" ><span class=\"ability-link\">[[File:Ability Evade.png|sub|link=Shion#Evade|40x40px |class=inline-icon invert-image]]</span>&#32;[[Shion#Evade|Evade]]</span> or <span class=\"ability-tooltip\" data-ability=\"Satsuriku Spree\" ><span class=\"error\">''Could not find 'Satsuriku Spree' in 'Abilities'. Check spelling and see [[Help:Cargo]] if the issue persists.''</span></span> while riding dismounts Shion and launches the bike along the ground. <span class=\"ability-tooltip\" data-ability=\"Execution\" ><span class=\"ability-link\">[[File:Ability Execution.png|sub|link=Shion#Execution|40x40px |class=inline-icon invert-image]]</span>&#32;[[Shion#Execution|Execution]]</span> cannot be activated while riding.\n** During the aerial targeting, <span class=\"ability-tooltip\" data-ability=\"Evade\" ><span class=\"ability-link\">[[File:Ability Evade.png|sub|link=Shion#Evade|40x40px |class=inline-icon invert-image]]</span>&#32;[[Shion#Evade|Evade]]</span> cannot be used and activating <span class=\"ability-tooltip\" data-ability=\"Satsuriku Spree\" ><span class=\"error\">''Could not find 'Satsuriku Spree' in 'Abilities'. Check spelling and see [[Help:Cargo]] if the issue persists.''</span></span> will completely remove the bike instead.\n* When launched along ground, the bike can slide along the walls if it hits them at low angle. Aerial launch will cause teh bike to explode immediately upon contact with terrain.\n* Any interception ability like [[stun]], [[hinder]], [[sleep]] etc. against Joyride will cancel her movement but automatically dismount her bike forward.\n** However, hack will also remove the bike directly. \n** <span class=\"ability-tooltip\" data-ability=\"Life Grip\" ><span class=\"ability-link\">[[File:Life_Grip_Icon.png|sub|link=Lifeweaver#Life Grip|40x40px |class=inline-icon invert-image]]</span>&#32;[[Lifeweaver#Life Grip|Life Grip]]</span> will dismount the bike on the ground. However it will completely remove bike if Shion in the air.\n* Reloads <span class=\"ability-tooltip\" data-ability=\"Kira Pistols\" ><span class=\"ability-link\">[[File:Ability Kira Pistols.png|middle|link=Shion#Kira Pistols|40x40px |class=inline-icon invert-image]]</span>&#32;[[Shion#Kira Pistols|Kira Pistols]]</span> after riding for 1.5 seconds. Aerial launch targeting period does not count towards this."
