        "hps": "",
        "ability keywords": "area of effect::hitscan::partial movement;;shion::reloads::transformation",
        "ability details": "* Primary fire, quick melee and Shion's other abilities are disabled while Satsuriku Spree is active.\n* While active, pressing primary fire activates \"Rush-Burst\", launching Shion in the target direction before dealing a burst of damage to all nearby enemies, pressing secondary fire activates \"Burst\" which causes has the same effect but without dashing.\n* During the burst, Shion locks on to all players and [[deployables]] (barriers, turrets, traps, etc.) in its range that are within line of sight, and fires toward each target at the same time.\n** Targets can be hit by shots aimed at targets behind them, causing them to block it and take the damage instead.\n** Barriers block shots, but do not prevent line of sight for acquiring targets.\n* Being [[hindered]] or otherwise locked out of movement abilities, such as during <span class=\"ability-tooltip\" data-ability=\"Life Grip\" ><span class=\"ability-link\">[[File:Life_Grip_Icon.png|sub|link=Lifeweaver#Life Grip|40x40px |class=inline-icon invert-image]]</span>&#32;[[Lifeweaver#Life Grip|Life Grip]]</span>'s grace period, will cause Rush-Burst to instead activate Burst.\n* Being [[hacked]] temporarily disables both Rush-Burst and Burst, but does not end the ability."
      },
